354	## 解決方案 4️⃣ : 加強保底計時器的狀態檢查
355	
356	### 問題
357	保底計時器被清除後，在某些情況下仍可能被觸發，導致重複揭示。
358	
359	### 當前代碼 (第 1699-1715 行)
360	
361	```typescript
362	private SetupRivalFireAnimationReveal(spine: sp.Skeleton, trackEntry: sp.spine.TrackEntry): void {
363	    const revealIndex = this.m_pendingRivalRevealIndex;
364	    const revealAmount = this.m_pendingRivalRevealAmount;
365	    const revealDisplayIndex = this.m_pendingRivalRevealDisplayIndex;
366	
367	    this.m_pendingRivalRevealIndex = -1;
368	    this.m_pendingRivalRevealDisplayIndex = -1;
369	    this.StartRivalRevealDelay(revealIndex, revealAmount, revealDisplayIndex);
370	    this.ClearRivalRevealFallback();
371	
372	    this.SetupRivalAnimationCompleteListener(spine, trackEntry);
373	
374	    // 設置保底計時器（避免動畫異常未回調時卡死）
375	    this.SetupRivalRevealFallbackTimer(trackEntry, revealIndex, revealAmount, revealDisplayIndex);
376	}
377	```
378	
379	### 解決方案
380	
381	**修改 `UpdateRivalRevealFallbackTimer()` 方法** (第 1129-1146 行)
382	
383	```typescript
384	/**
385	 * @ch 對手射擊保底揭示計時器（避免動畫異常未回調時卡死）
386	 */
387	private UpdateRivalRevealFallbackTimer(deltaTime: number): void {
388	    if (!this.m_rivalRevealArmed) {
389	        this.ClearRivalRevealFallback();
390	        return;
391	    }
392	
393	    this.m_rivalRevealFallbackTimer -= deltaTime;
394	    if (this.m_rivalRevealFallbackTimer <= 0) {
395	        const index = this.m_rivalRevealIndexCache;
396	        const amount = this.m_rivalRevealAmountCache;
397	        const displayIndex = this.m_rivalRevealDisplayIndexCache;
398	
399	        this.ClearRivalRevealFallback();
400	        this.ClearRivalRevealDelay();
401	
402	        // 只有在索引有效且當前狀態允許時才揭示
403	        if (index >= 0 && (this.m_state === 'rival_reveal' || this.m_state === 'waiting_player')) {
404	            console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 對手揭示保底觸發，狀態: ${this.m_state}, 索引: ${index}`);
405	            this.RemoveAvailableIndex(index);
406	            this.RevealRivalSelection(index, amount, displayIndex);
407	        } else if (index >= 0) {
408	            console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 對手揭示保底觸發但狀態不對，忽略。狀態: ${this.m_state}, 索引: ${index}`);
409	        }
410	    }
411	}
412	```
413	
414	**同樣修改 `UpdatePlayerRevealFallbackTimer()` 方法** (第 1179-1193 行)
415	
416	```typescript
417	/**
418	 * @ch 更新玩家射擊保底揭示計時器（避免動畫異常未回調時卡死）
419	 */
420	private UpdatePlayerRevealFallbackTimer(deltaTime: number): void {
421	    this.m_playerRevealFallbackTimer -= deltaTime;
422	    if (this.m_playerRevealFallbackTimer <= 0) {
423	        const index = this.m_playerRevealIndexCache;
