## 解決方案 2️⃣ : 改進動畫失敗回退邏輯

### 問題
當動畫播放失敗時，某些情況下不會設置完成標記，導致遊戲卡住。

### 當前代碼 (第 1614-1628 行 - 對手動畫失敗)

```typescript
private HandleRivalAnimationFailed(animation?: string): void {
    this.m_currentRivalAnimation = this.rivalStandbyAnimation;
    this.m_currentRivalLoop = true;
    this.m_pendingRivalReset = false;

    // 只在特定條件下設置完成標記
    if (this.m_state === 'finished' && animation === this.rivalLoseAnimation) {
        this.m_rivalLoseAnimationCompleted = true;
        this.CheckAndCloseBonusGame();
    }

    if (this.m_pendingRivalRevealIndex >= 0) {
        this.RevealRivalSelectionImmediately();
    }
}
```

### 解決方案

**修改 `HandleRivalAnimationFailed()` 方法** (第 1614-1628 行)

```typescript
private HandleRivalAnimationFailed(animation?: string): void {
    this.m_currentRivalAnimation = this.rivalStandbyAnimation;
    this.m_currentRivalLoop = true;
    this.m_pendingRivalReset = false;

    // 如果在 finished 狀態下失敗動畫失敗，直接標記為完成
    // 這樣即使特定動畫缺失，遊戲也不會卡住
    if (this.m_state === 'finished') {
        console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 對手動畫在 finished 狀態下失敗: ${animation}, 強制標記為完成`);
        this.m_rivalLoseAnimationCompleted = true;
        void this.CheckAndCloseBonusGame();
    }

    if (this.m_pendingRivalRevealIndex >= 0) {
        this.RevealRivalSelectionImmediately();
    }
}
```

**新增同樣邏輯到玩家動畫失敗處理** (在約 1360 行，尋找 `SetupPlayerSpineAnimation`)

在 `PlayPlayerAnimation()` 方法中添加失敗處理：

```typescript
private PlayPlayerAnimation(animation: string, loop: boolean, forceRestart = false): void {
    if (!animation) {
        return;
    }

    if (animation === this.playerFireAnimation
        && (forceRestart || this.m_currentPlayerAnimation !== animation || this.m_currentPlayerLoop !== loop)) {
        this.PlayPlayerShootAudio();
    }

    if (!forceRestart && this.m_currentPlayerAnimation === animation && this.m_currentPlayerLoop === loop) {
        return;
    }

    const spine = this.m_playerSpine;
    if (!spine) {
        console.warn('[BonusGameControll] playerSpine 為 null，無法播放動畫');
        // 如果在 finished 狀態，標記為完成
        if (this.m_state === 'finished') {
            this.m_playerVictoryAnimationCompleted = true;
            void this.CheckAndCloseBonusGame();
        }
        return;
    }

    const trackEntry = this.SetupPlayerSpineAnimation(spine, animation, loop);
    if (!trackEntry) {
        console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 玩家動畫設置失敗: ${animation}`);
        // 如果在 finished 狀態，標記為完成
        if (this.m_state === 'finished') {
            this.m_playerVictoryAnimationCompleted = true;
            void this.CheckAndCloseBonusGame();
        }
        return;
    }

    // ... 其餘代碼保持不變
}
```

