## 解決方案 4️⃣ : 加強保底計時器的狀態檢查

### 問題
保底計時器被清除後，在某些情況下仍可能被觸發，導致重複揭示。

### 當前代碼 (第 1699-1715 行)

```typescript
private SetupRivalFireAnimationReveal(spine: sp.Skeleton, trackEntry: sp.spine.TrackEntry): void {
    const revealIndex = this.m_pendingRivalRevealIndex;
    const revealAmount = this.m_pendingRivalRevealAmount;
    const revealDisplayIndex = this.m_pendingRivalRevealDisplayIndex;

    this.m_pendingRivalRevealIndex = -1;
    this.m_pendingRivalRevealDisplayIndex = -1;
    this.StartRivalRevealDelay(revealIndex, revealAmount, revealDisplayIndex);
    this.ClearRivalRevealFallback();

    this.SetupRivalAnimationCompleteListener(spine, trackEntry);

    // 設置保底計時器（避免動畫異常未回調時卡死）
    this.SetupRivalRevealFallbackTimer(trackEntry, revealIndex, revealAmount, revealDisplayIndex);
}
```

### 解決方案

**修改 `UpdateRivalRevealFallbackTimer()` 方法** (第 1129-1146 行)

```typescript
/**
 * @ch 對手射擊保底揭示計時器（避免動畫異常未回調時卡死）
 */
private UpdateRivalRevealFallbackTimer(deltaTime: number): void {
    if (!this.m_rivalRevealArmed) {
        this.ClearRivalRevealFallback();
        return;
    }

    this.m_rivalRevealFallbackTimer -= deltaTime;
    if (this.m_rivalRevealFallbackTimer <= 0) {
        const index = this.m_rivalRevealIndexCache;
        const amount = this.m_rivalRevealAmountCache;
        const displayIndex = this.m_rivalRevealDisplayIndexCache;

        this.ClearRivalRevealFallback();
        this.ClearRivalRevealDelay();

        // 只有在索引有效且當前狀態允許時才揭示
        if (index >= 0 && (this.m_state === 'rival_reveal' || this.m_state === 'waiting_player')) {
            console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 對手揭示保底觸發，狀態: ${this.m_state}, 索引: ${index}`);
            this.RemoveAvailableIndex(index);
            this.RevealRivalSelection(index, amount, displayIndex);
        } else if (index >= 0) {
            console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 對手揭示保底觸發但狀態不對，忽略。狀態: ${this.m_state}, 索引: ${index}`);
        }
    }
}
```

**同樣修改 `UpdatePlayerRevealFallbackTimer()` 方法** (第 1179-1193 行)

```typescript
/**
 * @ch 更新玩家射擊保底揭示計時器（避免動畫異常未回調時卡死）
 */
private UpdatePlayerRevealFallbackTimer(deltaTime: number): void {
    this.m_playerRevealFallbackTimer -= deltaTime;
    if (this.m_playerRevealFallbackTimer <= 0) {
        const index = this.m_playerRevealIndexCache;
        const isWin = this.m_playerRevealIsWinCache;
        const amount = this.m_playerRevealAmountCache;
        const displayIndex = this.m_playerRevealDisplayIndexCache;

        this.ClearPlayerRevealFallback();

        // 只有在索引有效且當前狀態允許時才揭示
        if (index >= 0 && this.m_state === 'player_reveal') {
            console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 玩家射擊動畫保底觸發，索引: ${index}`);
            this.RemoveAvailableIndex(index);
            this.RevealPlayerSelection(index, isWin, amount, displayIndex);
        } else if (index >= 0) {
            console.warn(`[BonusGameControll] 玩家射擊保底觸發但狀態不對，忽略。狀態: ${this.m_state}, 索引: ${index}`);
        }
    }
}
```

